OL,5,G1510 Kirstie and Phil's Love It or...
OL,6,     F...List It: Kirstie Allsopp and
OL,7,     FPhil Spencer help a couple on the
OL,8,     Foutskirts of Leeds. Karl loves
OL,9,     Ftheir home's idyllic location, but
OL,10,     FPaul finds it too isolated and
OL,11,     Fwants to move.
OL,12,G1615 A Place in the Sun
OL,13,     FBeverly and her mum Margaret are
OL,14,     Flooking for a rural house with
OL,15,     Fspace for family visits in Umbria
OL,16,     Fin Italy, for Beverly's budget of
OL,17,     F#150,000. Sara Damergi shows them
OL,18,     Ffive great options.
