OL,5,G1720 A Place in the Sun
OL,6,     FRachel and John can't wait to find
OL,7,     Fa holiday home for all their
OL,8,     Ffamily to enjoy, in the town of
OL,9,     FOliva on the stunning Valencian
OL,10,     Fcoastline. Ben Hillman shows them
OL,11,     Fwhat their #100k can buy.
OL,12,G1820 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FThe competition kicks off at The
OL,14,     FRed Lion in Charing Heath, Kent,
OL,15,     Fwhere the B&Bers are treated to a
OL,16,     Fmasterclass in hospitality. And
